author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-WD-40 Company Q2 Earnings Per Share $1.05
text:
April 6 (Reuters) - WD-40 Co:
* WD-40 COMPANY REPORTS SECOND QUARTER 2018 FINANCIAL RESULTS
* Q2 SALES ROSE 5 PERCENT TO $101.3 MILLION * FOR FY 2018 DILUTED EARNINGS PER SHARE IS EXPECTED TO BE BETWEEN $4.07 AND $4.14
* SEES 2018 NET SALES BETWEEN $407 MILLION AND $415 MILLION
* SAYS ‍FY 18 NET INCOME IS PROJECTED TO BE BETWEEN $56.6 MILLION AND $57.5 MILLION​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
